1
00:00:04,020 --> 00:00:09,480
We must know that Sahaja Yoga is a living
process.

2
00:00:09,480 --> 00:00:20,060
It is the same type of a process by which
a seed sprouts into a tree.

3
00:00:20,060 --> 00:00:26,770
It is a living process.

4
00:00:26,770 --> 00:00:33,480
So it is God’s job.

5
00:00:33,480 --> 00:00:36,539
I mean He has to do it.

6
00:00:36,539 --> 00:00:37,539
It is not your job.

7
00:00:37,539 --> 00:00:42,924
To sprout the seed is His job.

8
00:00:42,924 --> 00:00:52,170
But the problem comes in because, at this
stage where human being is the seed, he has

9
00:00:52,170 --> 00:00:55,210
freedom, they have freedom.

10
00:00:55,210 --> 00:01:03,410
With that freedom they can spoil His manifestation,
His working.

11
00:01:03,410 --> 00:01:08,280
So the first thing one has to remember that
we must have wisdom about it.

12
00:01:08,280 --> 00:01:17,409
The first point of wisdom is that it is God
Almighty who is going to do this job.

13
00:01:17,409 --> 00:01:20,939
We are not doing it.

14
00:01:20,939 --> 00:01:28,950
You cannot sprout the seed, then how can you
sprout your seed also?

15
00:01:28,950 --> 00:01:41,969
And in that wisdom we must learn one thing
and know, within ourselves, that you are part

16
00:01:41,969 --> 00:01:45,200
and parcel of the whole process.

17
00:01:45,200 --> 00:01:55,810
Though you have your own freedom, freedom
also is a part and parcel of the same process.

18
00:01:55,810 --> 00:01:57,920
You are not separated from God.

19
00:01:57,920 --> 00:02:02,039
You do not have any separated entity.

20
00:02:02,039 --> 00:02:05,549
You are part and parcel of that whole process.

21
00:02:05,549 --> 00:02:06,549
Alright?

22
00:02:06,549 --> 00:02:13,000
So to think that you have to decide something
about it is also wrong.

23
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:19,450
You are in the same machinery, brought to
this stage when you are given freedom for

24
00:02:19,450 --> 00:02:21,890
your further evolution.

25
00:02:21,890 --> 00:02:30,740
So at this stage, when you have your freedom,
you must know that freedom wants to be given

26
00:02:30,740 --> 00:02:36,840
to you to understand the value of freedom.

27
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:46,020
And in that freedom, you must understand what
is glorious for you.

28
00:02:46,020 --> 00:02:53,579
Once you understand that, then you tell yourself
that, “Now, see: I have to become something

29
00:02:53,579 --> 00:02:54,579
more.

30
00:02:54,579 --> 00:03:01,900
That’s why God has done this, only thing
I have to do is to completely coordinate,

31
00:03:01,900 --> 00:03:08,819
cooperate and surrender to His will, so that
I become."

32
00:03:08,819 --> 00:03:13,100
This is the first preparation we have to make.

33
00:03:13,100 --> 00:03:26,780
In that surrendering, you will do the greatest
thing because by that you do not interfere

34
00:03:26,780 --> 00:03:28,989
with His work.

35
00:03:28,989 --> 00:03:37,730
Unless and until you surrender you cannot
have the wisdom.

36
00:03:37,730 --> 00:03:44,159
So first of all you understand this, through
your little wisdom that you have, and then

37
00:03:44,159 --> 00:03:46,890
you’ll have the full wisdom.

38
00:03:46,890 --> 00:03:53,019
First of all, understand this with the little
wisdom that you have, that, without surrendering

39
00:03:53,019 --> 00:03:56,890
you will be obstructing the ways of God.

40
00:03:56,890 --> 00:03:57,890
He knows what is good for you.

41
00:03:57,890 --> 00:04:04,999
He wants to give you the highest which you
cannot achieve yourself.

42
00:04:04,999 --> 00:04:09,230
He’s going to give you the highest.

43
00:04:09,230 --> 00:04:11,439
If you want to achieve it, you cannot achieve
it.

44
00:04:11,439 --> 00:04:13,060
It is His doing.

45
00:04:13,060 --> 00:04:18,799
It is His daan (दान), as you call it,
His gift to you.

46
00:04:18,799 --> 00:04:31,740
In that case you must know that [the] best
way to achieve it is to allow His working

47
00:04:31,740 --> 00:04:34,590
to work out.

48
00:04:34,590 --> 00:04:45,660
Now when you think of surrendering, first
of all the brain wave starts working.

49
00:04:45,660 --> 00:04:50,990
“What do I surrender?”

50
00:04:50,990 --> 00:04:52,590
You think by surrendering, say, your material
wealth.

51
00:04:52,590 --> 00:04:53,590
That’s not what He wants.

52
00:04:53,590 --> 00:04:54,590
It’s all wealth He has given to you.

53
00:04:54,590 --> 00:04:58,430
What is He going to do [with that]?

54
00:04:58,430 --> 00:05:04,419
It’s [not] equal to even a dust particle
of His feet.

55
00:05:04,419 --> 00:05:15,840
So that one is not going to help.

56
00:05:15,840 --> 00:05:34,349
Sometimes you may feel that, “I should give
my intelligence,” or that is what is asked.

57
00:05:34,349 --> 00:05:38,379
Nobody wants to have your idiots and stupid
people!

58
00:05:38,379 --> 00:05:44,270
So you don’t give up your intelligence.

59
00:05:44,270 --> 00:05:49,150
Then some people think that, “I give up
my heart."

60
00:05:49,150 --> 00:05:51,580
Some people say it.

61
00:05:51,580 --> 00:05:56,430
We don’t want heartless people either.

62
00:05:56,430 --> 00:06:09,340
Then some people will say that, “Mother,
we’ll give up our relationships with others."

63
00:06:09,340 --> 00:06:15,410
That also is not needed.

64
00:06:15,410 --> 00:06:19,599
Because your heart should be there where it
is and the light has to come in your heart.

65
00:06:19,599 --> 00:06:23,080
What can you give your heart to whom?

66
00:06:23,080 --> 00:06:28,810
When the One who has given you the heart,
what’s the use of giving Him back the heart?

67
00:06:28,810 --> 00:06:29,810
Isn’t it?

68
00:06:29,810 --> 00:06:37,629
The One who has given you intelligence, what’s
the use of giving Him [it back]?

69
00:06:37,629 --> 00:06:41,830
Something that you have achieved yourself
has to be given.

70
00:06:41,830 --> 00:06:47,880
What have you achieved is your ego and your
super-ego.

71
00:06:47,880 --> 00:06:53,550
What you have achieved is nothing but your
ego.

72
00:06:53,550 --> 00:06:59,110
And this ego you have to give up, which is
a difficult task.

73
00:06:59,110 --> 00:07:08,340
Ego, if it comes out of money, material things,
it is better you give up some material things,

74
00:07:08,340 --> 00:07:10,530
not to God but somebody else.

75
00:07:10,530 --> 00:07:12,009
It’s better.

76
00:07:12,009 --> 00:07:17,939
If the material things are creating that ego.

77
00:07:17,939 --> 00:07:24,780
If your intelligence is creating ego that
you think you have a very high IQ, it’s

78
00:07:24,780 --> 00:07:28,530
better to bring it down a little.

79
00:07:28,530 --> 00:07:32,610
It is for you to judge.

80
00:07:32,610 --> 00:07:41,789
Watch yourself: what makes your ego bloated
up?

81
00:07:41,789 --> 00:07:52,180
If you could start looking at your ego you
will be amazed that any useless thing can

82
00:07:52,180 --> 00:07:57,780
bloat it and can also deflate it.

83
00:07:57,780 --> 00:08:02,490
It can get hurt from nothing at all.

84
00:08:02,490 --> 00:08:06,610
It becomes so important.

85
00:08:06,610 --> 00:08:10,409
Then the superego part of it also comes.

86
00:08:10,409 --> 00:08:13,800
That is what also you have to give up.

87
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:19,979
And in superego you can have your conditionings
due to your gurus and wrong types of doings

88
00:08:19,979 --> 00:08:26,199
and wrong types of conditionings [that] you
have had from childhood.

89
00:08:26,199 --> 00:08:32,070
Like, for example, somebody is a Catholic:
for him, Pope is everything.

90
00:08:32,070 --> 00:08:37,940
Or somebody is a Hindu: for him a particular
temple is everything.

91
00:08:37,940 --> 00:08:39,900
All these are conditionings.

92
00:08:39,900 --> 00:08:45,200
Why they are conditionings [is] that, without
finding out the truth about them, you have

93
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:48,500
just accepted them as it is.

94
00:08:48,500 --> 00:08:52,840
This is the simple thing.

95
00:08:52,840 --> 00:09:01,020
So if you can find out the truth about all
these things, you will give it up.

96
00:09:01,020 --> 00:09:02,270
You may, may not.

97
00:09:02,270 --> 00:09:04,790
There are many people who know the truth,
still they do not give up.

98
00:09:04,790 --> 00:09:07,340
You see, human beings are complicated stuff.

99
00:09:07,340 --> 00:09:10,560
Even if they know the truth they will not
give up.

100
00:09:10,560 --> 00:09:17,790
But supposing you try to find the truth about
all these things: then you may give, may not

101
00:09:17,790 --> 00:09:18,790
give.

102
00:09:18,790 --> 00:09:24,750
But going back into the whole thing, to find
out each and every thing, make a schedule

103
00:09:24,750 --> 00:09:28,960
of the whole thing that, ‘’Morning time
I’ll find out about this, and evening time

104
00:09:28,960 --> 00:09:36,020
about this,” The whole [of] your life you
will go on finding one by one, and ultimately

105
00:09:36,020 --> 00:09:41,580
you will find that you have gone now up to
the grave.

106
00:09:41,580 --> 00:09:45,200
So that procedure also is not going to help
you.

107
00:09:45,200 --> 00:09:53,410
By God’s grace you are Realised-souls and
you can find out in a second whether you are

108
00:09:53,410 --> 00:09:55,840
on the conditioning side or not.

109
00:09:55,840 --> 00:09:58,290
If your left is catching you are conditioned.

110
00:09:58,290 --> 00:10:05,010
If your right is catching you are on ego trip.

111
00:10:05,010 --> 00:10:06,010
Alright.

112
00:10:06,010 --> 00:10:12,170
So now you know very simple method is to know
that, through vibrations, you can find out

113
00:10:12,170 --> 00:10:17,320
[if] Mr Ego is there or superego is there
or you are wobbly.

114
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:30,900
This is the biggest thing we have got because
this is my preparation.

115
00:10:30,900 --> 00:10:40,460
My preparation is this, that, first give you
Realisation.

116
00:10:40,460 --> 00:10:42,410
First give you Realisation.

117
00:10:42,410 --> 00:10:47,870
Once you are Realised then I won’t have
to say much.

118
00:10:47,870 --> 00:10:54,170
If you are conditioned on the left side you
will get pains, this, that.

119
00:10:54,170 --> 00:10:59,640
If you are conditioned [on] right-hand side
you’ll have problems with health or something.

120
00:10:59,640 --> 00:11:04,750
So you will come to me and I will be able
to tell you.

121
00:11:04,750 --> 00:11:18,920
This is my own preparation: is to make you
alert and aware so that you have light to

122
00:11:18,920 --> 00:11:22,170
see things.

123
00:11:22,170 --> 00:11:28,060
Now your preparation should be to use this
awareness all the time.

124
00:11:28,060 --> 00:11:35,650
Further I will go to say that: to use this
knowledge within you all the time.

125
00:11:35,650 --> 00:11:42,680
That people forget.

126
00:11:42,680 --> 00:11:52,160
So the first [thing] we must know is that
this preparation has been done for us.

127
00:11:52,160 --> 00:12:01,080
We have got the vibrations.

128
00:12:01,080 --> 00:12:12,520
We have got the knowledge to verify and we
must use this.

129
00:12:12,520 --> 00:12:16,200
That you are in a new dimension is the first
acceptance.

130
00:12:16,200 --> 00:12:22,630
If you have that acceptance within you then
your judgement will be better.

131
00:12:22,630 --> 00:12:24,790
But this acceptance is missing.

132
00:12:24,790 --> 00:12:35,520
Now there is, in Sanskrit, a word, ‘abhyas’
, that every day doing the same thing in that

133
00:12:35,520 --> 00:12:43,370
manner you will remember that you are Realised
and that your awareness is not that of the

134
00:12:43,370 --> 00:12:46,490
awareness of ordinary people.

135
00:12:46,490 --> 00:12:55,280
So, first preparation is to prepare yourself,
to tell yourself that you have this new awareness

136
00:12:55,280 --> 00:13:01,820
within you, is to make yourself known.

137
00:13:01,820 --> 00:13:08,680
You see, in the University when you graduate,
there is a ceremony held for that.

138
00:13:08,680 --> 00:13:14,870
You have to go with a gown and they give you
a proper roll and all that.

139
00:13:14,870 --> 00:13:17,050
Why is it necessary?

140
00:13:17,050 --> 00:13:19,810
Because you may forget you are a graduate.

141
00:13:19,810 --> 00:13:24,110
(laughter) Yes!

142
00:13:24,110 --> 00:13:31,340
And that’s exactly what happens to you,
that you forget you are Realised-souls.

143
00:13:31,340 --> 00:13:40,080
I mean, we have had a ceremony in the sense
that everything we have done to prove that

144
00:13:40,080 --> 00:13:41,080
you are Realised-souls.

145
00:13:41,080 --> 00:13:50,440
But this is what is missing from our people,
that they cannot understand that they are

146
00:13:50,440 --> 00:13:57,890
Realised-souls, that they are people who are
on a level that nobody [else] is.

147
00:13:57,890 --> 00:14:06,800
You are twice-born people, who are very, very
rare.

148
00:14:06,800 --> 00:14:12,340
Very rarely you will find people who are twice-born.

149
00:14:12,340 --> 00:14:17,500
I mean, I found nobody – can you imagine?

150
00:14:17,500 --> 00:14:21,791
– all my lifetime, except for my father
and a few here and there.

151
00:14:21,791 --> 00:14:28,020
I mean they are not to be counted because
my father I chose and that’s how.

152
00:14:28,020 --> 00:14:37,500
So, first of all if you make yourself known
to your own intelligence that, “I am a Realised-soul!”

153
00:14:37,500 --> 00:14:45,470
you’ll be seeing that your priorities will
be changing very fast.

154
00:14:45,470 --> 00:14:53,760
Supposing somebody gives you a huge big property
or a huge big wealth.

155
00:14:53,760 --> 00:14:56,550
Immediately you become conscious of it.

156
00:14:56,550 --> 00:14:58,350
You start walking like this.

157
00:14:58,350 --> 00:15:03,930
When you are a student you walk like this.

158
00:15:03,930 --> 00:15:08,690
Suddenly you get the degree and walk like
this.

159
00:15:08,690 --> 00:15:11,180
(laughter) What about Realisation?

160
00:15:11,180 --> 00:15:15,360
So happy to see you here, very happy.

161
00:15:15,360 --> 00:15:17,050
May God Bless.

162
00:15:17,050 --> 00:15:19,300
What about your Realisation?

163
00:15:19,300 --> 00:15:21,800
You haven’t got your Realisation?

164
00:15:21,800 --> 00:15:25,990
Then what are you doing about it?

165
00:15:25,990 --> 00:15:38,750
This is the first preparation: is of identifying
that you are a Realised-soul.

166
00:15:38,750 --> 00:15:43,910
We have to talk in a different way – we
are Realised-souls now.

167
00:15:43,910 --> 00:15:48,300
We are people of a different knowledge.

168
00:15:48,300 --> 00:15:50,270
We are people of a different awareness.

169
00:15:50,270 --> 00:15:52,130
As I told you.

170
00:15:52,130 --> 00:15:58,340
Now see this beautiful building: we all are
enamoured by it and it looks very beautiful.

171
00:15:58,340 --> 00:16:00,500
It’s done so well, beautifully and is very
important for human beings.

172
00:16:00,500 --> 00:16:01,500
Alright?

173
00:16:01,500 --> 00:16:09,490
But for the Divine even this green leaf is
more important than the whole building put

174
00:16:09,490 --> 00:16:12,690
together and all such buildings put together.

175
00:16:12,690 --> 00:16:14,190
For the Divine.

176
00:16:14,190 --> 00:16:20,880
Because that leaf is living and a bird which
is more aware than that leaf is, is much more

177
00:16:20,880 --> 00:16:22,560
important to the Divine.

178
00:16:22,560 --> 00:16:30,320
So you, the human beings who are now aware
to this extent how much important you must

179
00:16:30,320 --> 00:16:31,320
be to Divine?

180
00:16:31,320 --> 00:16:36,900
How much God Himself must be interested in
you?

181
00:16:36,900 --> 00:16:38,730
Just think of it!

182
00:16:38,730 --> 00:16:49,880
Once you recognise this point, then relatively
you will also know that you are very important

183
00:16:49,880 --> 00:16:51,780
in God’s plan.

184
00:16:51,780 --> 00:16:56,110
Not world’s plan I am talking.

185
00:16:56,110 --> 00:17:00,320
(laughter) It is God’s plan.

186
00:17:00,320 --> 00:17:07,319
So all the forces of his blessings and all
his loftiness, all of them are with to help

187
00:17:07,319 --> 00:17:13,169
you, to support you, to give you whatever
you like.

188
00:17:13,169 --> 00:17:19,069
You are on the stage and they are looking
after you.

189
00:17:19,069 --> 00:17:26,039
I mean, now you have entered on the stage.

190
00:17:26,039 --> 00:17:37,870
But I find Sahaja Yogis, once they get Realisation,
I don’t know what happens to them.

191
00:17:37,870 --> 00:17:41,210
If they give up their ego then they become
like, absolutely, I don’t know what you

192
00:17:41,210 --> 00:17:42,860
call them…bananas?

193
00:17:42,860 --> 00:17:43,860
(laughter)

194
00:17:43,860 --> 00:17:54,850
Each one of you is the special one created
by God.

195
00:17:54,850 --> 00:18:04,080
Now you see for yourself, just think of yourself.

196
00:18:04,080 --> 00:18:13,429
I mean, you are the ones who know such a lot
about life.

197
00:18:13,429 --> 00:18:21,740
Even if you get a little bit possessed, doesn’t
matter.

198
00:18:21,740 --> 00:18:34,020
But you know that you are possessed.

199
00:18:34,020 --> 00:18:39,650
Now think of it.

200
00:18:39,650 --> 00:18:46,830
This is the second preparation one has to
have – is understanding that it is God Almighty

201
00:18:46,830 --> 00:18:51,950
Himself [who is] worried about you.

202
00:18:51,950 --> 00:18:58,769
He’s sent everybody to help you, “Go ahead!”

203
00:18:58,769 --> 00:19:05,929
So you don’t have to worry about your money,
you don’t have to worry about all other

204
00:19:05,929 --> 00:19:06,929
things.

205
00:19:06,929 --> 00:19:17,309
The third thing comes automatically 
that you don’t have to worry about all these

206
00:19:17,309 --> 00:19:18,480
things at all.

207
00:19:18,480 --> 00:19:20,049
They’ll be looked after.

208
00:19:20,049 --> 00:19:24,830
You all have been looked after, you know that.

209
00:19:24,830 --> 00:19:26,800
Everyone has been helped.

210
00:19:26,800 --> 00:19:37,620
But if you know that He is Almighty and He’s
compassion and that you have fallen into His

211
00:19:37,620 --> 00:19:40,570
grace – think of it!

212
00:19:40,570 --> 00:19:48,590
Establish yourself at that point.

213
00:19:48,590 --> 00:20:05,769
This is the preparation one has to have, that
He is the one who has given all this.

214
00:20:05,769 --> 00:20:17,720
Then, the modern Sahaja Yogis are specially
blessed because they have a ‘walkie-talkie’

215
00:20:17,720 --> 00:20:19,179
with them.

216
00:20:19,179 --> 00:20:30,210
Any problem that they have are handled in
form, in person!

217
00:20:30,210 --> 00:20:41,669
There was never such a blessing before.

218
00:20:41,669 --> 00:20:51,129
But ego is the point.

219
00:20:51,129 --> 00:20:53,370
To begin with it is ego.

220
00:20:53,370 --> 00:20:56,249
You have seen it.

221
00:20:56,249 --> 00:20:58,230
If you have ego you will not accept you are
a Realised-soul.

222
00:20:58,230 --> 00:20:59,230
Imagine, how silly it is!

223
00:20:59,230 --> 00:21:06,620
If you have a superego also you will not recognise
it.

224
00:21:06,620 --> 00:21:10,620
You will go back to the same position as you
were.

225
00:21:10,620 --> 00:21:16,860
You will never accept that you are a Realised-soul
if you have a superego.

226
00:21:16,860 --> 00:21:21,860
You’ll never accept, “Oh, how can it be,
Mother?

227
00:21:21,860 --> 00:21:24,179
After all I am an ordinary human being."

228
00:21:24,179 --> 00:21:27,370
