now.

465
00:41:09,820 --> 00:41:17,520
All of you believe in the heart, not in the
brain.

466
00:41:17,520 --> 00:41:22,890
That you are a Realised-soul, is first thing
you must tell your intelligence.

467
00:41:22,890 --> 00:41:29,670
